msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"You ate a lot of it too. You pushed yourself, didn't you?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:996

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"I felt like I had to take responsibility... but I guess I couldn't match up. You wound up eating most of it.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:997

msgid "Obviously we were both trying to let the other person eat less of it, but in the end, we both ate our fair share."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1000

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"You're looking kinda pale, Kazushi. We'd better get back.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1001

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"Wha...\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1002

msgid "No way! We still have about three more hours to kill."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1003

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"I'm fine! I'll pop into the general store and get a drink. That should help.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1006

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"Wait. I'm coming too.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1010

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"Hello.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1013

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"Miya-san, can we get something to drink? Something to clear the head and an upset stomach.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1018

msgid "{Miya}\n\"Welco...... What's wrong? You two don't look good.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1019

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"Miya-san, could you please tell the guy at the fish shop to stop selling Tuna Frappe snowballs for us?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1020

msgid "{Miya}\n\"Y... you two actually ate that? Hold on, I've got some good herbal tea that I can bring for you.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1021

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"Thank you, Miya-san.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1025

msgid "Miya-san went back inside the back room. Mizuki was feeling slightly better, so she looked around the store."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1028

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"Ooh!\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1029

msgid "And something on the shelf caught her eyes."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1032

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"So cute...\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1033

msgid "It looks like a pendant with a small stone dangling on it. The pendant looks like a dewdrop."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1034

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"Do you like cute stuff?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1037

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"Of course I do. I am a girl, you know.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1038

msgid "She was a little upset at my statement, but her attention was fixed on the pendant."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1041

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"How nice. I want to buy it.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1042

msgid "I looked at the price tag. It was quite expensive."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1045

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"Urk... Quite pricey. It's over my budget.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1046

msgid "{Miya}\n\"Do you like that?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1051

msgid "Miya-san returns with two cups of tea in his hands."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1052

msgid "{Miya}\n\"Drink this. You'll feel better.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1053

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"Whoa! This has got to be working!\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1054

msgid "This surely looks and smells like herbal tea. We began to sip on it with gratitude."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1057

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"It's so bitter! ...It'd better be working.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1058

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"Hmm. I'm kinda getting used to this tea's bitterness.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1059

msgid "We both sipped on the bitter tea. Our stomachs started to feel warm, and we both felt a lot better."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1062

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"I feel better now.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1065

msgid "{Miya}\n\"That's good.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1066

msgid "Miya-san picked up the pendant Mizuki was looking at."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1069

msgid "{Miya}\n\"This pendant is made from a stone found exclusively on this island. It's a natural stone we don't gather very often, which is why it's a bit expensive.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1070

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"I see. I guess this may be too much of luxury for me now.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1071

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"So you're not buying it?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1074

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"I want to, but I can't. It's a bit too much for me.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1075

msgid "Mizuki looks a bit sad but seems to give up for now. She continues to sip on the tea. She's quite a sport."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1076

msgid "{Miya}\n\"So, are you two on a date?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1079

msgid "{Mizuki}\n *PTTTTTBBBBBTTTTTT*"
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1082

msgid "She did it again. This time she did it on Miya-san."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1083

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"Ahh! Miya-san. I'm terribly sorry.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1084

msgid "{Miya}\n\"That's okay. Did I say something wrong?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1085

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"Do we look like we're on a date?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1088

msgid "{Miya}\n\"Yes. You two look good together.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1089

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"Really?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1092

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"Don't take that so seriously. Miya-san's a merchant so he has to be a good talker. This is how he sells things.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1093

msgid "{Miya}\n\"Oh, no. I really think you two look like a nice couple.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1096

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"Some nice shop talk, Miya-san.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1099

msgid "{Miya}\n\"Oh, Mizuki-chan. You are a shy girl, huh?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1102

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"Wha?! ...Argh! Let's go, Kazushi!\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1106

msgid "Flushed with embarrassment, Mizuki dashed out of the store."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1110

msgid "{Miya}\n\"Did I say something wrong?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1111

msgid "For my sake, it's a good thing that Mizuki left the store first."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1112

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"Miya-san, I have a favor to ask you...\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1115

msgid "{Miya}\n\"Hmm? What?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1121

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"Kazushi, you kept me waiting! What on Earth were you doing in there?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1122

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"I was just talking with Miya-san. That's all.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1125

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"So, what are we going to do now?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1126

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"Well...\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1127

msgid "We still have some time..."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1128

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"Let's go to the inlet!\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1136

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"I should have brought my swimsuit if we were heading to the beach.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1137

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"You were swimming naked before.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1140

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"You promised not to bring that up!\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1141

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"Okay, okay...\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1143

msgid "Mizuki walked barefoot on the beach toward the water. While running on tiptoe, she played with the waves lapping on the beach."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1144

msgid "She looked a little sad, but not too bothered that she couldn't go swimming now."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1145

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"You really like the water, don't you?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1148

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"I wouldn't even mind if I had to live in the sea.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1149

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"You used to be on the swim team, right? I heard you placed in nationals during junior high.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1150

msgid "I heard she was even in a magazine and drew a lot of attention."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1153

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"I didn't want to do it, but they forced me to.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1154

msgid "Mizuki replies with no interest in that particular subject."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1155

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"It's kind of wasting your talents like this, don't you think? You could have gone to the Olympics.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1158

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"Give me a break. I don't want to swim for competitions any more. That was hard - incredibly hard for me.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1159

msgid "Mizuki looks sad and upset."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1160

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"Hard training? How long did they make you swim for you to hate it?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1161

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"It's not that training was so hard. It's just...\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1162

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"What was hard then?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1165

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"It was...\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1166

msgid "Flushing slightly, Mizuki hesitated to continue talking."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1167

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"What is it? Don't leave me hanging. Did you get physically abused?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1170

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"What? Abused?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1171

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"Oh!! Was it sexual harassment?! Did your horny coach touch you?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1172

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"Sexual harassment? No! Nothing like that!\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1173

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"No? Are you sure? What is it then?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1176

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"No, nothing like that happened. It was...\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1177

msgid "Mizuki looks down, sticking her index fingers up together."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1178

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"I just couldn't deal with the boys' competition speedos.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1179

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"What?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1180

msgid "Boys' swimsuits? I have no clue what Mizuki is talking about."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1183

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"I'm talking about men's competition swimsuits! Swimsuits! Don't you think those are horrible?!\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1184

msgid "Mizuki leaned towards me, demanding my agreement."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1185

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"Well, I don't know. What do you think?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1188

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"Don't you think those things are way too small? They're so tight, and...\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1189

msgid "Mizuki, again, looks flushed. She may be picturing that thing packed in tight trunks."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1192

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"Being in the pool with those things - it was torture for me. I put up with it for three years!\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1193

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"Is that the reason why you gave up on swimming?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1196

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"You bet!\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1197

msgid "I guess it's true. She's not kidding, is she? This is way out of my league."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1200

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"It doesn't matter now, though, because I just want to swim for me. That's why I came to this island.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1201

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"If that's okay with you, that's okay with me.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1202

msgid "But I still kind of feel like she's wasting her talent."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1203

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"This island suits me perfectly. I can swim all year and I never have to see a man's improper speedo.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1204

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"This school used to only be for girls, huh?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1205

msgid "So this is why Mizuki chose this school. She didn't want to see men in speedos."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1206

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"Why did you join the swimming club in the first place?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1209

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"I was asked to join rather forcefully, and that was the quickest, easiest way to swim every day. There wasn't an ocean or river near us.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1212

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"The best we had nearby was a pool, so I joined a team in elementary school, but I never realized that the boy's swimwear in junior high would look that different.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1213

msgid "Mizuki shuddered as she visualized it in her mind. It seemed to be a big deal for her."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1216

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"Signing up for a gym or a private pool would have been too expensive, so I had no choice but to put up with going to my school's club.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1217

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"I guess I get the picture now.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1218

msgid "But one question."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1219

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"But that means you hadn't learned to swim since you were born or anything right? So what made you like swimming so much?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1220

msgid "I know you don't need a reason to like something, but there's usually some kind of motivation at the front. I wonder what it was for Mizuki."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1221

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"My motivator was dolphins.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1222

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"Dolphins?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1223

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"When I was in the third grade, my family took me to see a dolphin show.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1226

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"The dolphins were all adorable. I liked them instantly. Then, later on, I found out that you could swim with them in the sea too.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1227

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"On TV, I saw foreigners swimming with a dolphin. They looked like they were having so much fun that I got jealous.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1228

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"Then I said, \"I want to do that too!\".\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1229

msgid "Mizuki looks out at the horizon with her sparkling eyes."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1232

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"I also saw a movie based on the story of this guy. He could dive 100 meters deep without scuba gear on. I was stunned, thinking 'Wow, how could people do that?'\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1233

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"Then I wondered if you had to swim that well to swim with dolphins. So I thought I needed to become a good swimmer to swim with them... That's what got me started.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1234

msgid "Mizuki said that she started showing her natural talent for swimming immediately. But in fact, that wasn't what she really wanted to do."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1237

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"But the boys, showing everything in their trunks! What the hell's up with that? I didn't want to swim together with those things!\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1238

msgid "She looks pretty upset. It must have been a majorly traumatic experience for her."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1241

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"All I want is to swim with the dolphins in the sea. The emerald green sea, the deep blue ocean, any of the world's beautiful waters!\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1244

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"That's my dream.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1245

msgid "Mizuki was full of life when she talked about her dream. She looked more beautiful than usual, which made me hooked on her."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1248

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"Uh... You don't really care about this, do you?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1249

msgid "Suddenly Mizuki became quiet. Maybe she mistook my silence for indifference."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1250

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"You kidding? I'm impressed. That's a wonderful dream.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1253

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"You really think so?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1254

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"Yeah. I do.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1255

msgid "Swimming with the dolphins. It was a perfect picture for Mizuki. She fits right in there."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1256

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"Any dolphins in this sea around here?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1259

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"The fishermen have seen some dolphins stuck in the bay before, but I've never seen them for myself.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1260

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"It would be great if you could swim with them.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1263

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"When I do, you have to swim with me, Kazushi!\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1264

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"Me? No... not me.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1267

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"You'll be fine, you'll be fine. I'll make sure you can swim better. And I'll hold your hand too.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1268

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"I'm not a kid, you know.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1269

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"Yes, you are... as far as I'm concerned.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1270

msgid "Swimming with the dolphins. That would be fun - I'd love to do it then, sharing in Mizuki's dream."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1271

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"Then I have to practice swimming more first.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1272

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"That's right. I have to train you.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1273

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"Ugh... Sob... Oh, right.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1274

msgid "I recalled it as I was about to cry and took it out of my pocket."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1277

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"Here you go...\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1278

msgid "It is a little paper bag - something I got from Miya-san's store."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1281

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"What's this?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1282

msgid "Given the size of the bag, Mizuki could already guess what was in it."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1285

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"For me? Can I open it?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1286

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"Go ahead.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1288

msgid "She opens the bag and as expected, finds the pendant inside."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1289

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"How did you get this?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1290

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"I didn't steal it. I bought it.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1293

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"You bought it? But it was expensive.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1294

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"I talked the price down with Miya-san.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1295

msgid "And yet it was still pricy for me. In fact, I couldn't pay for it all at once, so now I've got to pay it off in installments."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1296

msgid "I owe Miya-san a massive favor."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1297

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"Miya-san said that little stone hanging there is a charm called a 'Mermaid's Tear'.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1300

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"A mermaid's tear?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1301

msgid "The truth is, it was the name that pushed me to actually buy the pendant for Mizuki - because a mermaid was my first impression of her."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1302

msgid "So I begged him to let me have it."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1303

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"I thought this pendant is a perfect fit for you.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1306

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"But I can't take something so expensive.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1307

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"Please take it. It's not like I can wear it, you know?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1310

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"But...\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1311

msgid "Mizuki looked stunned and a few tears welled up in her eyes. The pendant worked brilliantly as a surprise gift."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1312

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"I'll feel bad if you don't take it - it wouldn't look right on a guy anyways. Here, let me do it.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1313

msgid "I took the necklace form her hand and fastened it around her neck."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1314

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"Good!! I told you! It looks perfect on you!\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1317

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"You think so?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1318

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"Yes, So take it. Please?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1319

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"Okay... In that case, thank you.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1320

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"My pleasure.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1321

msgid "Mizuki carefully wrapped the pendant with her hands and glanced at me."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1324

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"Why are you so nice to me today? Buying me lunch and the present...\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1325

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"Why?...\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1326

msgid "I have to keep Mizuki away from school until things are ready for the party. That's why..."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1327

msgid "The present wasn't part of the plan, though. Present?"
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1328

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"Do you know about today, by any chance?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1329

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"What?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1330

msgid "Today... The reason I'd been keeping her away."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1331

msgid "Today is Mizuki's birthday. Everyone is now preparing to throw a surprise birthday party for her."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1332

msgid "By now, everything must be ready with food and presents."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1335

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"Is this my birthday present?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1336

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"Uh...\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1337

msgid "No...it's not your birthday present.\nI just saw how you longingly gazed at it."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1338

msgid "Your real present should be sorted and ready at the party."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1339

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"You knew it, huh? That's why you asked me out on a date?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1340

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"A date...?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1341

msgid "What have I done? I asked her out rather forcibly. We ate and strolled around together. Then I gave her a present."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1342

msgid "Good Lord! I'm already covering all the birthday events!"
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1343

msgid "And I did all this alone!"
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1344

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"Uh...\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1345

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"Happy birthday!!\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1346

msgid "Sorry, everyone. I got there first."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1349

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"No wonder. I found the whole thing very strange.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1350

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"I just wanted to surprise you.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1353

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"I was. Thank you. I feel so happy.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1356

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"I feel touched.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1357

msgid "I saw a wet drop glitter in the corner of her eye. I was astonished by her tear. I never expected her to cry."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1360

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"I'll treasure this.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1361

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"Yeah.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1362

msgid "I felt so embarrassed. Everything I did today would make me look extremely snobby."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1365

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\".........\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1366

msgid "Nonetheless, we ended up with a nice situation. The two of us alone on her birthday and she's happy with my present."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1367

msgid "What would a real couple do next?"
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1370

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"Oh...\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1372

msgid "Our arms accidentally brushed each other, and Mizuki jerked back away. I guess she was acting more conscious of me."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1373

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"Uh... Mizuki.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1376

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"Y-yes!? What can I do for you!?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1377

msgid "Politeness? She was extremely stiff."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1378

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"We are just, uh, pretending to be a couple, right?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1381

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"Y-Yes... D-Do you not want to do it anymore?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1382

msgid "Mizuki looks puzzled. I shake my head."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1383

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"N-no, no! The other way around!\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1386

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"The other way around?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1387

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"I mean. You and I...\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1388

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"Me and you...?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1389

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"I mean. Can you...\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1391

msgid "*BANG!*"
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1394

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"Wah! W-what's that?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1395

msgid "A huge firework sparkled in the sky above the school."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1396

msgid "{Kazushi}\n\"Oh...\""
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1397

msgid "It was the signal that preparations were done. We'd decided to signal it by fireworks since no one knew where we'd be at the time."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1398

msgid "And..."
msgstr ""

#: 20102:1399

msgid "{Mizuki}\n\"What's that? Has a war broken out?\""
msgstr ""

